dct_title_s: Fayal Pico and San Jorge, Azores
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, soundings, and spot heights. "Published according to Act of Parliament ... July 25th, 1849." "1855." Includes 8 cross sections. North oriented to the upper left. Historic Maps copy has label on verso: No. 1855.
dct_creator_sm: Vidal, A. T. E. (Alexander Thomas Emeric), 1792-1863
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Published ... at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty ; sold by R.B. Bate, agent for the Admiralty charts, 21 Poultry, 1849.
